caller_intent: The caller intended to speak directly with Heather Johnson, likely regarding an insurance-related matter.
resolution_steps: Informed caller Heather was unavailable but in the office.
Offered to leave a voice message for Heather.
Caller declined to leave a message and insisted on speaking to Heather.
Agent agreed to relay the caller's request to Heather.
summary: Caller attempted to reach Heather Johnson at Alliance Insurance. Agent confirmed Heather was in the office but unavailable, and the caller refused to leave a message. Agent committed to informing Heather of the call. No immediate resolution achieved, but follow-up was arranged.
